ğŸ“ Vim Text Editor
What is Vim?
Vim stands for Vi Improved. It is a mode-based terminal text editor.

ğŸ§  Vim Modes
Normal (Command) Mode â†’ Default mode

Insert Mode â†’ For typing text

Enter insert mode: i

Exit insert mode: Esc

